# 설계 (raw 99 hive-cli-canonical + raw 36 fixpoint)
@cli_canonical hive-exec mac_runaway_watchdog [--threshold-mb N] [--dry-run] [--selftest]. 도구는 /Users/ghost/core/hive/tool/mac_runaway_watchdog.hexa (per "전부 hive cli 로 구현").
@detection_patterns 4 cmdline 패턴: hexa_interp.real / hexa.real / kick_dispatch.hexa / "nexus kick" + RSS > threshold_mb.
@false_positive_guard self-exclusion (cmdline contains "mac_runaway_watchdog" OR "ps -eo pid,rss,command") — watchdog 자신 + ps invocation 제외.
@threshold_default 4096 MB (4GB) — Mac 24GB physmem ÷ 6 = 17% per-process cap. 보수적: TUI/daemon 보존 + 진짜 runaway 잡음.
@kill_mechanism `kill -9 <pid>` per-PID — blanket pkill 금지 (TUI 보호).
@safety_floor `--threshold-mb < 100` reject + raw 66 trailer (실수 0 threshold 방지).

